  <!-- EN: Directly damaging explosions, incendiary weapons and EMP blasts are capable of detonating an ADM without risking your pawn's life. -->
  <BDM_Tips.tips.0>会造成伤害的爆炸，例如燃烧弹和EMP，能够用来远程引爆ADM。</BDM_Tips.tips.0>
  <!-- EN: Sometimes it's easier to spot the ADM carrier casing than the mine itself. -->
  <BDM_Tips.tips.1>有的时候布雷弹的浅蓝色整流罩比ADM本身更显眼。</BDM_Tips.tips.1>
  <!-- EN: You can safely disarm an ADM with enough intellectual and crafting skill, and with sufficient manipulation and sight capability. -->
  <BDM_Tips.tips.2>拥有高智识和手工，且拥有完好操作能力和视力的小人能够安全的拆除ADM。</BDM_Tips.tips.2>
  
